caption:
Our new season collection, spotted, in the wild. A day in the life in DISSH (what else?). 

Transporting you from the cityscape and taking you to the Australian seaside (your out-of-office, on). This latest drop is designed to see you through every day – no matter what’s in store. Welcoming a fresh new colour palette, brought to life in new takes on effortless DISSH classics. 

Same time tomorrow? 

Documented across the bustling streets of Sydney to the Yamba seaside. Images captured by Kristina Yenko. Motion captured by Ramsay Hosn. 
#DISSH
